
/*
 * The code snippet demonstrates the use of the [add] slot to append nodes to a destination node. It retrieves nodes from the [.args] node using [get-nodes] and adds them as children to the destination node specified by the [add] slot's expression. 
 * 
 * 1. [add] - Appends nodes to the destination node specified by its expression.
 * 2. [get-nodes] - Retrieves nodes from the [.args] node to be added to the destination.
 */
add:x:+
   get-nodes:x:@.args/*
